.TH AUXFONT 1 "June 2026" "A/UX Workstation" "Local Commands"
.SH NAME
auxfont \- switch the desktop font theme everywhere at once
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B auxfont
.IR theme
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B auxfont
rewrites every font consumer on the desktop in one pass: the Rxvt and
XTerm resources in
.IR /.Xdefaults ,
the fvwm menu Font, WindowFont, and every -fn flag in
.IR /.fvwmrc ,
the auxtop-x and dialc-x launchers, and the gtk style font in
.IR /.gtkrc .
It then merges the X resources and syncs the disk.  Restart fvwm and
open new terminals to see the change.
.SH THEMES
.TP
.B profont
terminals profont15, window chrome profont12 (the default look)
.TP
.B profont-big
terminals profont17
.TP
.B profont-small
terminals profont12
.TP
.B fixed
the original 7x13 / lucidatypewriter look
.SH ADDING FONTS
The XmacII server is R4-era and reads SNF only.  Compile BDFs with
bdftosnf(1), run mkfontdir, add fonts.alias entries, xset fp rehash,
then add a theme case to this script.
.SH FILES
/usr/lib/X11/fonts/profont, /.Xdefaults, /.fvwmrc, /.gtkrc
.SH SEE ALSO
auxtop(1), dialc(1)
